(2530, 898, '_fields', 'a:4:{s:10:"your-email";s:18:"tumaca@comcast.net";s:9:"your-name";s:19:"Vincent DAlessandro";s:12:"your-subject";s:11:"Solar Light";s:12:"your-message";s:724:"I''m responding to an email I received from Nancy following my purchase of the Deneve LED Solar Flag Pole Light - New and Improved for 2014 - Even Brighter, More Power, More Light Spread and More Flag Coverage - LED Downlight.  The email asked that I respond to you directly before posting a review on Amazon.\n\nInitially I was very pleased with this light, which I installed on 4/12.  However, as the days (and nights) have passed, I am less pleased.  The light is nowhere near as bright as it was the first four nights of operation.  Suddenly the light appeared to be much dimmer and has remained that way.  All the LEDs continue to be illuminated but the light the product is casting is not as bright.  Very disappointing.\n";}'),
