(2628, 918, '_fields', 'a:4:{s:10:"your-email";s:18:"tumaca@comcast.net";s:9:"your-name";s:19:"Vincent DAlessandro";s:12:"your-subject";s:11:"Solar Light";s:12:"your-message";s:1596:"In response to my earlier message to you weeks ago, I got an automated message saying that customer service would get back to me within 24-48 hours.  Since that did not happen I assume it is then OK for me to write a negative review of your flag pole solar light on Amazon?  \n\nBelow is the initial email I received from you after purchasing the solar light.  I contacted you in response to this message signed by Nancy.  The light performed well for 4 days but since has been extraordinarily dim.  Wondering if this is an inherent problem with the product.\n\n\n\n\n Dear Vincent DAlessandro,\n\nWe are contacting you to ensure that you are completely satisfied with your order with Deneve on Amazon.\n\nIf there''s any reason you don''t feel compelled to leave us a positive Product or seller rating, please contact us in advance. We know you have many choices, and are deeply honored to earn your business.\n\nWe are committed to 100% customer satisfaction, plain and simple. If you''re not satisfied, neither are we. It is equally critical to us to continue providing the same high quality service and products to others as we''ve been providing you.\n\nWhen you''re ready, could we trouble you to leave us a positive product review on the "Review Product" link below?\nHere are the details for Amazon order: 116-6247597-0767443\n\n    Deneve? LED Solar Flag Pole Light - New and Improved for 2014 - Even Brighter, More Power, More Light Spread and More Flag Coverage - LED Downlight L (Leave Product Review)\n\nThank you for supporting us! We hope to see you around soon.\n\n\nBest Regards,\n\nNancy\n\nCo-Founder - Deneve";}'),
