(718, 3, '2013-10-24 17:53:57', '2013-10-24 17:53:57', '<div>Deneve warrants your product to be free from mechanical defects. Deneve guarantees a full refund minus shipping if product is returned within the 30 day period of purchase. No refunds after the 30 day return policy has expired.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div>All returns and exchanges should be mailed to:</div>\r\n<div>Deneve</div>\r\n<div>340 E. First St. #335\r\nTustin, CA 92781</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div>No R.A. (return authorization) number is needed. Please include original or a copy of the original Invoice/Receipt or Packing Slip along with all the original items and original packaging. Items must be in undamaged, unmarked, unscratched condition. Please include a short note about why you are not satisfied if possible.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div>Deneve  reserves the right to refuse product returns deemed damaged or unusable. Please remember to include contact info, so we can get back to you. Allow 1 to 2 weeks for delivery.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div><strong>Shipping Information</strong>\r\nAll purchases from this Web Site are made pursuant to a shipment contract. As a result, risk of loss and title for items purchased from this Web Site pass to you upon delivery of the items to the carrier. You are responsible for filing any claims with carriers for damaged and/or lost shipments.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div>Orders placed after 4pm will ship the next business day. We do not ship outside the United States (Continental United States), Hawaii, Puerto Rico, Guam and Alaska only. For security reasons, we do not ship to P.O. boxes or APO/FPO addresses. Shipments will go UPS ground unless otherwise specified.</div>', 'Return Policy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '705-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-24 17:53:57', '2013-10-24 17:53:57', '', 705, 'http://deneveusa.com/archives/718', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
