(869, 1, '2014-03-26 05:53:13', '2014-03-26 05:53:13', '<P><B>INTRODUCING THE BEST GO-ANYWHERE ULTRASONIC PORTABLE COOL MIST HUMIDIFIER THAT FITS IN YOUR PURSE OR COAT POCKET.  Exclusively designed by Deneve.</B>\r\n\r\n</P><P>Never worry again about lost AC adapters, tanks, bottles or canisters. Never let spilling water or water bottle fitment issues frustrate you again. Our tested design also tips over much less, too.\r\n\r\n</P><P><B>PROVIDES RELIEF ALL YEAR LONG</B></P><P>Relief from dry air, cold, flu, cracked skin in the winter and cold weather. Use as mister during summer or hot weather. Even use a diffuser for aromatherapy. (Only use Water-Soluble aromatic oils. Do Not Use Pure Essential Oil). Or even as a moisturizer for your hands by holding hands over mist. \r\n\r\n</P><P><B>SUPER EASY TO USE</B></P><P>\r\nDrop into water source. Power it on. Balanced design reduces tipping over. And that''s it!\r\n\r\n</P><P><B>SUPER EASY TO MAINTAIN</B></P><P>\r\n1) Wipe with damp cloth as often as you''d like.<BR>\r\n2) On weekly basis: when powered off, wipe or soak the stalk portion with a 9 parts water to 1 part bleach solution.  Rinse with water-dampened cloth.  Dry fully before reusing.<BR>\r\n3) Replace internal filter wick every 3 months max.<BR>\r\n</P><P><B>SUPER DISCREET</B></P><P>\r\nGentle output covers up to 20 sq. ft. of personal space.  Perfect for using in a cubicle without distracting neighbors.</P><P>\r\n<B>CHARITY AND GOODWILL </B></P> <P> With your help, Deneve is committed to making our best effort to influence the world in a positive manner. We donate a portion of proceeds to charity.</P> \r\n<P><B>SUPER WARRANTY</B></P> \r\n<B>Deneve is exclusively marketed on Amazon by Deneve only. Be sure you receive authentic product packaging to ensure 1 year satisfaction guarantee.</B>', 'Ultrasonic Cool Mist Pocket Humidifier', 'ALLEVIATE ALLERGIES, DRYNESS, AND RELIEVES COLD & FLU SYMPTOMS ANYWHERE with USB power with the Deneve Personal Ultrasonic Humidifier\r\nMost hassle-free, worry-free, trouble-free, and portable personal humidifier on the market today. Simply plug into nearly any USB power source, fill up a glass or water bottle with water, and insert humidifier. Small enough to easily fit into a coat pocket, let alone in your luggage.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ultrasonic-cool-mist-pocket-humidifier', '', '', '2014-03-26 05:53:13', '2014-03-26 05:53:13', '', 0, 'http://deneveusa.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=869', 0, 'product', '', 0),
