 Resistant String of Clear G40 Globe Lights. These lights are perfect for weddings, birthday parties, and other gatherings. These are ideal for adding a cozy atmosphere, or a charming and festive accent, to a casual evening under the stars.\n\nRecreate stunning Italian Tuscan landscapes right at home. Create Perfect Everlasting Memories for a Lifetime; Dine or host parties under your own strand of stars. A perfect accent to any function, indoor or outdoor.\n\nTo extend a warm welcome to your guests, suspend them under tents, patios, awnings, or umbrellas. The Green wiring blends in perfectly with trees and bushes. Drape them on trees or in entryways.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '677-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-05-05 18:18:24', '2014-05-05 18:18:24', '', 677, 'http://deneveusa.com/archives/934', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
