(756, 1, '2013-12-13 18:05:35', '2013-12-13 18:05:35', '<P><B>COME HOME TO THE DELIGHTFUL AND EXHILARATING MAGICAL EFFECT</B> of the Deneve Starry String Lights.  With wires spun & drawn from pure copper which are thin, bendable & sturdy, along with our industry-leading extra-long transparent lead cord, our lights will truly look like floating stars since the wires nearly disappear out of sight.</B></P><P>\r\nEnvision a warm and welcoming holiday landscape and setting with the radiant accent of our starry string lights.  Dotted with points of lights, the strings of bendable fine wire conform to any shape your imagination desires.  Use one or more together to drape dressings, wrap plants or wreaths, or animate and illuminate glass cloches on your table.  Create perfect everlasting memories for a lifetime; dine or host parties under your own strand of stars. \r\n</P><P>\r\n<B>SPECS</B></P><P> \r\nLED Bulb Count: 120</P><P> \r\nBulb Spacing: 2 in.</P><P>\r\nLength of Lead Cord: 12 ft.</P><P>\r\nLighted Length: 20 ft.</P><P>\r\nWire Material: Copper</P><P>\r\nLED Color: Amber</P><P>\r\nIncludes 110V to 240V Power Adapter</P><P> \r\n<B>CAUTION</B></P> \r\n<P>LED''s are waterproof and weather-resistant and can be momentarily submerged in water.  The LED''s can withstand rain and snow.  However, the AC adapter is not waterproof. When using outdoors, please ensure the AC adapter is fully protected from the elements.</P><P>\r\n<P><B>CHARITY & GOODWILL</B></P>\r\n<P>With your help, Deneve is committed to making our best effort to influence our nation & the world in a positive and life-changing manner. We donate a portion of proceeds from all sales to charity.</P>  \r\n<P><B>WARRANTY</B></P>\r\n<P>Deneve is exclusively marketed on Amazon by Deneve only. 3 year satisfaction guarantee, only from Deneve!</P>', 'Starry String Lights 120 Warm White LEDs on Copper Wire', '<ul>\r\n	<li>FILL YOUR SPACE AND YOUR LIFE WITH LIGHT WITH THE WARM DELICATE GLOW OF OUR STARRY STRING LIGHTS!</li>\r\n	<li>Lab-Tested as Weather-Resistant and Water-Proof, these lights are the perfect solution for permanent, year-round ideas. Allow your imagination to run wild with ideas to complement, decorate, and accent indoors and outdoors.  Dress up or breathe new life into ordinary or tired household items and decor, as well as backyard or garden motifs</li>\r\n	<li>Our 2014 version includes a 12 feet long heavy-duty clear lead cord (an original design by Deneve), thicker copper wire, and universal 110V to 240V Power Adapter which provide the ultimate combination of flexibility and durability  for quick installation, placement, configuration and design anytime, anywhere.  See your idea come to life in just a few minutes!</li>\r\n	<li>Eco-Friendly and power-sipping LED bulbs Means Less Concerns and Worrying with Power Consumption- Spend More Time Unleashing Your Creativity, and enjoying the splendor of your efforts with loved ones!</li>\r\n	<li>Backed by a 1-year satisfaction guarantee! Portion of net proceeds donated to charity!</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'starry-string-lights-120-warm-white-leds-on-copper-wire', '', '', '2014-04-05 00:27:19', '2014-04-05 00:27:19', '', 0, 'http://deneveusa.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=756', 0, 'product', '', 0),
