 minimum, we help you pay things forward by making charitable contributions.  We strive to donate a portion of a product''s net proceeds to a charitable organization who is relevant to the product, as often as once every 3 months.  So that your money will work most effectively, we scrutinize the recipients of our donations by analyzing their overhead &amp; efficiency on trustworthy watchdog resources such as <a title="http://www.charitywatch.org" href="http://www.charitywatch.org/" target="_blank">charitywatch.org</a> and <a title="charitynavigator.org" href="charitynavigator.org" target="_blank">charitynavigator.org</a>.  We urge you to do the same when considering your own personal donations.\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '560-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-07-31 03:37:03', '2013-07-31 03:37:03', '', 560, 'http://deneveusa.com/archives/649', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
